                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#181d27] leading-[28.8px] mb-2.5">Calls at Once</h3>
                    <p class="text-base text-[#535862] leading-[27.2px]">No more busy lines! Sophiie can handle up to 10,000 calls simultaneously, keeping customers happy and engaged.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-4">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl pt-[37px] px-5 pb-8 text-center">
                    <div class="count-up text-[50px] font-semibold text-[#36a5e1] leading-[50px] mb-[21px]" data-value="90" data-suffix="%">90%</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#181d27] leading-[28.8px] mb-2.5">Faster Response Time</h3>
                    <p class="text-base text-[#535862] leading-[27.2px]">Sophiie handles enquiries, providing quick answers and boosting customer satisfaction.</p>
