<section class="py-20 bg-white" x-data="{ active: 0 }">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:flex lg:gap-16">
        <!-- Left: Heading -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/3 mb-10 lg:mb-0">
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently asked<br/>questions</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500">Find quick answers to common questions about how Sophiie AI works.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Accordion -->
        <div class="lg:w-2/3 space-y-3">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <button @click="active = active === 0 ? null : 0" class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 pr-4">How does Sophiie handle incoming calls?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand flex-shrink-0 transition-transform" :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 0 }" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 0" x-collapse x-cloak class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Sophiie can either ring your phone first and answer only if you miss the call, or pick up instantly, depending on what works best for your business. This ensures every caller receives a prompt, professional response, whether you're available or not.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <button @click="active = active === 1 ? null : 1" class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 pr-4">Does Sophiie work after hours and on weekends?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand flex-shrink-0 transition-transform" :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 1 }" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 1" x-collapse x-cloak class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Absolutely! Sophiie is available 24/7, so your business stays open even when you're off the clock. She never takes a sick day, never goes on holiday, and always answers calls: day or night, rain, hail, or shine!
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <button @click="active = active === 2 ? null : 2" class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 pr-4">What happens if Sophiie can't answer a customer's question?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand flex-shrink-0 transition-transform" :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 2 }" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 2" x-collapse x-cloak class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    If Sophiie doesn't have an answer, she records the enquiry and sends it to you for review. You can then add the response to her knowledge base, so next time a customer asks the same question, Sophiie will know exactly how to answer.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <button @click="active = active === 3 ? null : 3" class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 pr-4">How does Sophiie know what to say to my customers?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand flex-shrink-0 transition-transform" :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 3 }" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 3" x-collapse x-cloak class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Sophiie is trained with a knowledge base and follows pre-set responses based on your business needs. You can customise her answers anytime to ensure she provides accurate information. Once trained, she never forgets and delivers the correct response every time.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <button @click="active = active === 4 ? null : 4" class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 pr-4">Can Sophiie handle different types of businesses?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand flex-shrink-0 transition-transform" :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 4 }" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 4" x-collapse x-cloak class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Yes! Sophiie is designed for any service-based industry, including trades, medical, legal, finance, automotive, health &amp; wellness, and more. She adapts to your business needs with custom responses tailored to your services.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <button @click="active = active === 5 ? null : 5" class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 pr-4">Can Sophiie handle multiple calls at once?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand flex-shrink-0 transition-transform" :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 5 }" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 5" x-collapse x-cloak class="px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Yes! Sophiie can handle up to 10,000 calls simultaneously, ensuring no customer is ever left waiting. Whether it's one call or a thousand, Sophiie answers instantly, so your business never misses an opportunity.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

